notesStmt.note: Aṣṭaka 1: According to Poleman, leaves 1-3 accented, leaf 5 unnumbered and written on r only, leaves 6-20 accented from 6-9r, leaves 15-61 accented from 15-33 only. Colophon: Samvat 1801 śake 1666 āṣāḍhe māse śuklapakśe caturdaśyam guruvāsare tadine pustakam samāptam. yādṛśam pustakam dṛṣṭvā tādṛśam likhitam mayā. yadi śuddham aśuddham vā mama doṣona diyate. idam pustakam gangārama bhaṭṭagāmena likhitam svārtham parārtham ca.
Aṣṭaka 2: According to Poleman, leaves 1-49, 42-71, 71-72, 72-101, 1-76, 62-101 are all accented.
Aṣṭaka 3: According to Poleman, leaves 1-76, 62-100, 1-12 are accented.
